{
  "texts": [
    "We don't want to block that.",
    "Designer 1: If not too tall, then maybe something mid back height?",
    "Designer 2: I think the height of the back should be carefully scaled -supportive but not so high that it obscures what is behind too much.",
    "Designer 1: Or shoulder height for support Designer 1: With arm support Designer 2: Agreed on shoulder height.",
    "Swiveling is good -also moving -like on casters may provide flexibility."
  ]
